{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1b4d086e80","title":"满江红·和郭沫若同志","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ea1858f4a","index":0,"year":1963,"month":1,"day":9,"articleId":"1b4d086e80"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"389b6b843a","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"寰球，指全地球。"},{"id":"f4e60ddeed","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"蚂蚁缘槐夸大国，唐李公佐小说《南柯太守传》载：有个叫淳于梦的人，梦见自已在“大槐安国”做了附马，又在南柯郡当了20年太守，权势显赫。等到妻子死后，官被解除，槐安国用车子送他回家。醒后追寻梦游之处，原来是在一株住着一堆蚂蚁的大槐树穴中。"},{"id":"14c59c84d1","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"此撼树，，大蚂蚁。撼，摇动。这是对不自量力的人的喇笑。唐韩愈《调张籍》：“此婷撼大树，可笑不自量。”"},{"id":"07d66bb6e6","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"正西风落叶下长安，飞鸣销，长安，唐朝都城，即今西安市。前半句化用唐贾岛《忆江上吴处士》一诗“秋风生渭水，落叶满长安”句，表示秋风已起虫子不好过了。鸣铺，古时一种射出去能发声音的箭，也叫响箭。这里借喻革命力量的声讨。"},{"id":"14303ed793","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"立极，树立准则。"},{"id":"eebe73bf4e","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"朵犬味尧堪笑止，是夏代最末一个帝王，是个暴君。汉邹阳《狱中上梁王书》：“之犬可使尧”（参见《汉书·邹阳传》）。堪笑止，可笑已极。"},{"id":"f4bade93bd","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","index":7,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"泥牛入海，宋僧道原《景德传灯录》：“我见两个泥牛斗入海，直至如今无消息。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"551ddc1606","type":"title","text":"满江红·和郭沫若同志","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"389b6b843a","type":"paragraph","text":"小小寰球则，有几个苍蝇碰壁。喻嘴叫，几声读厉，几声抽拉。蚂蚁缘槐夸大国批撼树谈何易。正西风落叶下长安司，飞鸣铺。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"f4e60ddeed","type":"paragraph","text":"多少事，","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"14c59c84d1","type":"paragraph","text":"从来急；","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"07d66bb6e6","type":"paragraph","text":"天地转，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"14303ed793","type":"paragraph","text":"光阴迫。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"eebe73bf4e","type":"paragraph","text":"一万年太久，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"f4bade93bd","type":"paragraph","text":"只争朝夕。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"10761b5708","type":"paragraph","text":"四海翻腾云水怒，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"fb502dc584","type":"paragraph","text":"五洲震荡风雷激。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"ed6df14a4e","type":"paragraph","text":"要扫除一切害人虫，","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"8e2a129aec","type":"paragraph","text":"全无敌。附：郭沫若原词","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"ea81efc128","type":"subtitle","text":"满江红","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"54287d5b2b","type":"paragraph","text":"沧海横流，","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"833df07e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"方显出英雄本色。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"2a95ab4c91","type":"paragraph","text":"人六，","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"3cffcb45b4","type":"paragraph","text":"加强团结，","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"ecb0b5f8d0","type":"paragraph","text":"坚持原则。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"d88af13295","type":"paragraph","text":"天塔下来掌得起，","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"2c93679659","type":"paragraph","text":"世披摩奖扶之直。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"370f5ae526","type":"paragraph","text":"听雄鸡一唱遍衰中，","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"},{"id":"a2ba3464fc","type":"paragraph","text":"东方白。太阳出，冰山滴；真金在，艺销锈？有雄文四卷，为民立极则。乘犬吹尧堪笑止园泥牛入海无消息。迎东风革命展红旗，乾坤赤。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80"}],"page":{"id":"959c67027b","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b4d086e80","start":334,"end":336}}}},"__N_SSG":true}